parameters.name: BucketAcl
parameters.description:
The access control list (ACL) of the bucket.

*   **private** (default)
*   **public-read-write**
*   **public-read**

parameters.name: BucketName
parameters.description:
The name of the bucket.

This parameter can contain 3 to 50 characters in length and can contain only lowercase letters, digits, and hyphens (-). The name cannot start or end with a hyphen (-).

parameters.name: Comment
parameters.description: The remarks. The remarks are 0 to 128 characters in length.

parameters.name: EnsRegionId
parameters.description: The ID of the region where the node is located. If this parameter is not specified, the node is the global default node.

parameters.name: LogicalBucketType
parameters.description: Single-node storage. Set the value to sink.
